Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: ovs-access-monitor
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: OVS Access Bridge Failover Monitor
Home-page: https://www.starlingx.io
Author: Wind River Systems, Inc.
Author-email: starlingx-discuss@lists.starlingx.io
License: Apache-2.0

Description:
ovs-access-monitor is a systemd service that monitors the health of the
OVS agent pod and manages PF interface membership in the ovs0 Linux bridge.
When the pod is healthy, the PF is removed from the bridge (traffic flows
through the pod's veth). When the pod is unhealthy or absent, the PF is
re-added to provide fallback connectivity.

Platform: UNKNOWN
